  <summary date="2021-07-23T13:04:32Z" status="Introduced in House">FAIR Leave Act or the Fair Access for Individuals to Receive Leave Act

This bill repeals the limit on the aggregate number of workweeks of family and medical leave that spouses employed by the same employer may be entitled to during any 12-month period. The current limit is 12 aggregate workweeks.</summary>
